    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Inner Peace",
      "uuid": "78d18d1d1e7d4887a9d1f8549fdbfbf4",
      "x": -1440.5814585137919,
      "y": 407.116087504872,
      "width": 665.723667633647,
      "height": 283.115361013124,
      "z_value": -9.956000000000024,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "0.1.0 - The Fluff Era\n0.0.2 - The Era where we fixed the typo in the version counter\n0.0.3 - The Interlinking Era\nThere is also one named Two, its not a descendant of One or something, it's its name \"Two\"\n0.0.5 - The Breath of Air Era\n0.0.4 - Is missing - is its actual name, not that it is missing, its named \"0.0.4 - Is Missing\", and came after 0.0.5\n0.1.0 - The Dawn of a new Era of Mankind\n0.2.0 - The Prestige Era\n0.3.0 - The Expressive Era\n0.5.0 - The Other Era, Not the untold one."
    },
